{"tid":1344424,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有咩活動？","createTime":"2019-07-21T22:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T22:58:53.000Z","uid":265498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edd68c1340d999be88cfb3e155787de1c387921c","tid":1344424,"uid":265498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:39:46.000Z","msg":"尋晚去咗上環啲海味舖買嘢，由朝玩到晚，行完西又行翻去東，由頭行到尾又尾行到頭 <br />\n依邊就瘋狂開炮<br />\n果邊元朗就無差別攻擊<br />\n<br />\n今日你哋唔係想繼續翻工啊？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5eb0139ff1204694d016498e26d39be7ad8f09","tid":1344424,"uid":194177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:40:04.000Z","msg":"（有片有字）4分鐘解釋警黑何君堯疑合作打市民，求文宣組散開<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344349</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成晚無訓剪起左一條綜合琴晚元朗發生咩事嘅片<br />\n包括事件疑似由嶺大校董何君堯及經濟日報石禮泉引起，<br />\n更加有孕婦受害！<br />\n另外亦簡單解釋左警察點樣放起白衫人<br />\n希望一朝早可以send比你地親戚朋友睇<br />\n因為tvb嘅篇幅同有嘅片真係好少<br />\n求大家share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7236cdb688138edb00397f0000c36ea4c15879bc","tid":1344424,"uid":267822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日地鐵運作受阻返唔到工</span>"},{"pid":"00e0a343e5ef6801c3c63c98003bf906692137d4","tid":1344424,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a97e05f30f21e0acd034e21b8c3c8670a0cdf333","tid":1344424,"uid":265498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":